description:
Progress has been made on the 12 Trial Chamber farm, and today we ride the full thing to check out how it works. We look into the possibilities for making a semi-automatic killing chamber for it.

We head to the Villager Trading system to listen to the new audio cues that indicate the different trade times. Then we do a quick exploration trip to check out and collect the new 1.24.4 content.
